  "privacyTitle": "Privacy Policy",
  "privacyHeading": "AgroBravo Enterprises - Commitment to Your Privacy",
  "privacyIntro": "AgroBravo Enterprises, headquartered in Ames, Iowa (USA) with a branch in Brazil, values the trust you place in us. This policy describes how we handle your personal information.",
  "privacyS1Title": "1. Information Collection",
  "privacyS1Body": "We collect information when you use our services, fill out forms or participate in our missions. This includes full name, email, phone, company name, payment information and details required for travel logistics (such as passport and visas).",
  "privacyS2Title": "2. Data Use",
  "privacyS2Body": "We use your data to:\n• Process and manage technical missions and trips.\n• Send updates about the market and new business opportunities.\n• Provide personalized support during events.\n• Comply with legal and regulatory obligations.",
  "privacyS3Title": "3. Sharing and Protection",
  "privacyS3Body": "We do not share information with third parties, except when necessary to provide services (logistics partners, hotels, government agencies) or by legal obligation. We adopt encryption practices and security measures to protect your privacy.",
  "privacyS4Title": "4. Mobile Application",
  "privacyS4Body": "Our app may collect photos and videos provided by you for social functionality and mission recording. This data is not shared for external commercial purposes and you can request deletion of your account and data at any time.",
  "privacyS5Title": "5. Your Rights",
  "privacyS5Body": "You have the right to access, rectify or request deletion of your personal data. To exercise these rights, contact us through the support channels in the application.",
  "privacyLastUpdated": "Last updated: April 22, 2025",

